  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to compare the peak dose relative bronchoprotection offered by
      levosalbutamol and racemic salbutamol in mild to moderate asthmatics preselected into two
      groups on the basis of their beta-2 adrenoreceptor polymorphisms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
